parameters:
The resistance fighters of Norvanna are a gathering of volunteers, admired by
everyone. I hear that many warriors come from the floating continent, of course,
but also from the ground nations like Grales and Rue-Belle.

Everyone is suffering under Lucia's steel soldiers and Valentina, which has
formed a military alliance with Jupiterino. But this city, Norvanna, is the only
one that stands firm against the imperial capital.

Man: "Hilda is a terrifying sorceress who devours people. She swallows them
whole, starting from the head. But this town is safe because the resistance
fighters are protecting us."
